spie_ericcantona_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/2024_bobbygillespie_ericcantona_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/2024_bobbygillespie_ericcantona_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/2024_bobbygillespie_ericcantona_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/2024_bobbygillespie_ericcantona_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/2024_bobbygillespie_ericcantona_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/primal-scream">Primal Scream</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bobby-gillespie">鲍比·吉莱斯皮 (Bobby Gillespie)</a>与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/eric-cantona">埃里克·坎通纳 (Eric Cantona)</a>合作创作了一首这位前足球运动员为巴勒斯坦人创作的歌曲。</p><p>两人在伦敦国王广场的一场音乐会上联手演唱了歌曲《Give Us A Ticket》。您可以查看下面的视频。</p><p>吉莱斯皮在官方 Primal Scream Instagram 上写道：“昨晚，我很荣幸能与我的朋友@ericcantona 一起演唱他为巴勒斯坦写的歌曲，名为《给我们一张票》。</p><p> “埃里克刚刚和他的乐队一起巡演——他们的声音让人想起<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/serge-gainsbourg">塞尔日·甘斯布</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tom-waits">汤姆·威茨</a>和查尔斯·波迪莱尔（如果他穿着 7 号球衣），多么棒的一场音乐会。谢谢你埃里克。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C55gcqQt5YK/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" backgrou