st-image" alt="泰勒·斯威夫特和亚伦·德斯纳" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/2024_taylorswift_aarondessner_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/2024_taylorswift_aarondessner_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/2024_taylorswift_aarondessner_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/2024_taylorswift_aarondessner_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/2024_taylorswift_aarondessner_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/2024_taylorswift_aarondessner_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-national">《国家报</a>》的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/aaron-dessner">亚伦·德斯纳</a>承认“永远感激”参与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>新专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/taylor-swift-the-tortured-poets-department-lyrics-tracklist-3619454">《The Tortured Poets Department》</a>的制作。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/taylor-swift-the-tortured-poets-department-lyrics-tracklist-3619454">《受折磨的诗人部》评论：罕见的失误</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位吉他手兼制作人<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swifts-the-tortured-poets-department-here-are-the-full-album-credits-3619931">与他的兄弟布莱斯·德斯纳 (Bryce Dessner)</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bleachers">Bleachers 乐队</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jack-antonoff">杰克·安东诺夫 (Jack Antonoff)</a>一起参与了斯威夫特的第 11 张录音室作品。</p><p>戴斯纳与这位歌手有着悠久的合作历史，此前她制作了她之前的三张专辑和“重新录制”的 LP，包括 2020 年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/taylor-swift-folklore-album-review-2713965">《Folklore》</a>和 2021 年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/taylor-swift-evermore-review-2835933">《Evermore》</a> 。</p><p>斯威夫特还为国家乐队 2023 年专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-national-first-two-pages-of-frankenstein-review-3434616">《弗兰肯斯坦的前两页》</a>中的《奥尔科特》提供了人声和歌词。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C58OCiBAVSZ/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 5