25" target="_blank" rel="noopener">写道</a>：“泰勒·斯威夫特真是个假游戏玩家……她写了一整首关于<em>《堡垒之夜》</em>的歌曲，但拼写错误。”</p><p> 《The Tortured Poets Department》发布后，谷歌搜索“ <em>Fortnite</em> ”的<a href="https://trends.google.com/trends/explore?date=now%201-d&amp;q=fortnite" target="_blank" rel="noopener">数量激增</a>。</p><p>自从<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/heres-the-official-tracklist-for-taylor-swifts-the-tortured-poets-department-3583090">二月份《The Tortured Poets Department》的曲目列表被分享</a>以来，一直有关于泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 与<em>《堡垒之夜》</em>合作的传言，虽然尚未宣布任何具体消息，但斯威夫特本人已<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tortured-poets-department-taylor-swift-shares-easter-eggs-guests-and-teases-timetable-release-schedule-3619457">暗示发行周将带来许多惊喜。</a></p><p>在此之前， <em>《堡垒之夜》</em>正在庆祝<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/coachella">科切拉音乐节</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/coachella-returns-to-fortnite-with-sabrina-carpenter-doja-cat-j-balvin-and-grimes-3615886">第二个周末</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/doja-cat">Doja Cat</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sabrina-carpenter">Sabrina Carpenter</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bleachers">Bleachers</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ice-spice">Ice Spice</a>等人都参与其中。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/fortnite-fans-want-a-taylor-swift-collab-following-release-of-the-tortured-poets-department-fortnight-3620070">在《The Tortured Poets Department》</a>首次在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上发布后，《堡垒之夜》粉丝希望泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 合作。</p> ;
